name: 般若波羅蜜多💎(稀有.收藏品)
bio: Shalom! I'm 般若波羅蜜多💎(稀有.收藏品). I enjoy licking doorknobs, glaring at the neighbour's cat, and fighting the patriarchy. I once dreamed of being a Ventriloquist. Now I can be found summoning ghosts all day. We can be friends, but keep the ultra purrsonal stuff to yourself, please.
